{"title":"1.Micrisoft-Hyper-V虚拟化安装与入门学习","slug":"虚拟云容/虚拟化/Hyper-v/1.Microsoft-Hyper-V虚拟化安装与入门学习","date":"2019-05-22T06:36:30.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T05:39:02.683Z","url":"2019/5-22-482.html","path":"api/articles/2019/5-22-482.html.json","covers":["https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200716164918.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200717105409.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200717110233.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200716162414.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200717111747.png"],"content":"<p>[TOC]</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h4 id=\"0x00-前言简述\"><a href=\"#0x00-前言简述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0x00 前言简述\"></a>0x00 前言简述</h4><p>安装环境:<br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Host Name:                 WEIYIGEEK</span><br><span class=\"line\">OS Name:                   Microsoft Windows 10 专业版</span><br><span class=\"line\">OS Version:                10.0.18363 N/A Build 18363</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Step 1.Windows 10 下 Hyper-V 安装<figure class=\"image-box\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200716164918.png\" alt=\"WeiyiGeek.Hyper-V管理器\" title=\"\" class=\"\">\n                <p>WeiyiGeek.Hyper-V管理器</p>\n            </figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Step 2.采用Hyper-V 快速创建程序创建虚拟机<br>程序地址:<code>%ProgramFiles%\\Hyper-V\\VMCreate.exe</code>, 打开后此处选择本地安装源进行安装，此处可以采用镜像ISO文件或者其它Hyper-V导出的磁盘映像文件;</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"image-box\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200717105409.png\" alt=\"WeiyiGeek.虚拟机创建\" title=\"\" class=\"\">\n                <p>WeiyiGeek.虚拟机创建</p>\n            </figure>\n<ul>\n<li>Step 3.在启动前序需要进行启动顺序调整和关闭安全启动，然后再启动创建的虚拟机(安装系统此处略去查看我前面的文章后者百度即可);</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"image-box\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200717110233.png\" alt=\"WeiyiGeek.启动顺序调整和创建虚拟机\" title=\"\" class=\"\">\n                <p>WeiyiGeek.启动顺序调整和创建虚拟机</p>\n            </figure>\n<ul>\n<li>Step 4.与VMware类似的您也可以新建立一个新的外部网络交换机即<code>设置桥接、NAT、或者直连</code>；</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"image-box\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200716162414.png\" alt=\"WeiyiGeek.VirtualSwitch\" title=\"\" class=\"\">\n                <p>WeiyiGeek.VirtualSwitch</p>\n            </figure>\n<ul>\n<li>Step 5.虚拟机安装成功<figure class=\"image-box\">\n                <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/WeiyiGeek/blogimage/2020/1/20200717111747.png\" alt=\"WeiyiGeek.安装成功\" title=\"\" class=\"\">\n                <p>WeiyiGeek.安装成功</p>\n            </figure></li>\n</ul>\n","comments":true,"excerpt":"[TOC]","categories":[{"name":"Virtualization","path":"api/categories/Virtualization.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Virtual","path":"api/tags/Virtual.json"}]}